        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.List<LineAction>>> getAclActions()
        Description copied from interface: SynthesizerInput
        Mapping: hostname -> aclName -> lineNumber -> lineAction
        This mapping contains only the acls that are required for the operation this SynthesizerInput is being used for. Specifically, for ACL-reachability this should contain all ACLs, while for other reachability queries this will only contain ACLs that a packet could reasonably encounter (e.g. ACLs assigned to interfaces).
        Specified by:
        getAclActions in interface SynthesizerInput
